<h2>Marketing Executive (Exp: 0.5 - 2 years)</h2>
<p>As part of this role, you would:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Coordinate with operation teams to identify the requirements for ongoing part-time internships wherein college students devote 20 hours a week and work remotely around their location.</li>
    <li>Develop an expansion strategy to get maximum applications of college students for the ongoing part-time internships. This may include – Market research on colleges, Identifying skill set required, selection criteria, digital and non-digital marketing channels.</li>
    <li>Foster long-term relationships with training & placement officers or campus relations department of various colleges across India.</li>
