    <li>Experience of working a startup is preferred.</li>
    <li>Must be aggressive towards driving the targets.</li>
    <li>Must have impeccable verbal and written communication skills (Both English and Hindi).</li>
    <li>Must have excellent relationship management skills.</li>
    <li>Critical business thinking is essential.</li>
</ol>
